allorsUnifiedGood.name: EINSA CDA14C
allorsUnifiedGood.description:
The Self-Propelled Conveyor Belt Loader, model CDA-14, is a robust heavy duty unit designed for efficient loading and off-loading of airfreight, mail and baggage on all commercial aircraft in operation today.  
It is available in 8m or 6m boom length versions and incorporates hydrostatic transmission, diesel engine in an easily removable power pack module and hydraulic steering.
